aboutMe.title: About Me
aboutMe.content:
Committed and Highly responsible, with a strong sense of accountability. 

 Quick to learn, good communication, and a team-oriented mindset. 
 Knowledgeable in Java, C#, HTML, CSS, React, React-Native, Java-script, SQL, 
 noSQL, Containering(Docker and Kubernets), Azure Cloud Computing, Git, GitHub 
 Actions, Postman, Insomnia. 

 Focused on writing efficient and optimized code to build high-performance 
 applications. Experienced in minimizing unnecessary loops, optimizing database 
 queries, and leveraging indexed columns to enhance overall system performance. 

 Core Skill: Java - Spring Boot

myHealth.title: minha-saude.com
myHealth.description: A health management application that allows users to track their medical history, appointments, and medications. Built with React Native for cross-platform compatibility and integrated with a backend API for data storage and retrieval.

restaurantDelivery.title: Restaurant Delivery
restaurantDelivery.description: A food delivery application that connects users with local restaurants. Built with React and Node.js, featuring real-time order tracking and a user-friendly interface.
